As a Surfs Up Candle Box Subscriber, youll receive a package filled with special surprises four times a year  Spring, Summer, Fall and Winter  that will feature items like mason jar candles, paint can candles, bath and body products, accessories and other fan-favorites!*
Your Spring box will include a mixture of soft, inviting scents and popular florals to help you make the much anticipated transition from winter into April Showers and May Flowers!
Get ready for the sun, beach and sand with some of our signature scents and vintage, ocean vibes with your Summer box.
Fall Scaries?! You wont have anything to fear when you receive your Fall box that taps into your love of sweater weather, hot apple cider and pumpkin patches.
Have you been naughty or nice? At Surfs Up, youre automatically on our nice list and your Winter box will be your favorite present! Snuggle up to the yulelog (real or fake!) with our best winter scents - think fresh pine needles, hot cocoa, mistletoe, holiday cookies and more!
*Box will not include every item listed or pictured and may include other items not listed or shown. The items listed and pictured are meant to provide an idea of what may be included season to season. Actual contents will vary, but we dont think youll be disappointed!
  By subscribing, you are agreeing to being a member and getting charged for at least three subscription boxes. See terms and conditions for more detailed information. 
The one-time purchase is valid for a single box. The box you receive will depend on the date of purchase. See below schedule for more details on which box to expect.
Automatic Payment and Shipping Schedule for Subscribers
You will be charged for your first box at time of checkout, and it will be shipped within 7-10 business days. Once you subscribe, you will be automatically placed on a standardized seasonal, 3-month payment and shipping schedule starting with your second box. See below for payment and shipping schedules based on the date you originally subscribed. 
If you subscribe between January 1st and April 1st, you will receive your first box (the Spring box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on June 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
If you subscribe between April 2nd and July 1st, you will receive your first box (the Summer box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on September 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
If you subscribe between July 2nd and October 1st, you will receive your first box (the Fall box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on December 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
If you subscribe between October 2nd and December 31st, you will receive your first box (the Winter box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on March 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
Terms and Conditions
Due to COVID-19 safety guidelines, members may experience shipping delays. The Surfs Up Candle subscription box is a service that will be billed based on the option chosen. The two options we offer are 1) seasonally, four times a year with an automatic charge of $29.99 + $7 flat rate shipping using the payment method provided or 2) a one-time charge of $64.00 + free shipping for a single subscription box based on the season in which you purchase (see detailed calendar for exact dates). Foreign exchange or transaction fees may apply for non US customers. If youd like to cancel your subscription, you can do so after your third subscription box is fulfilled. After that, you can cancel no later than14 days prior to the next billing period. To cancel please contact Surfs Up Candle Subscription Box Customer Service at subscriptions@surfsupcandle.com.
  Please note: subscription box returns will not be accepted, and once the subscription is charged it cannot be refunded or cancelled. Cancellations must occur 14 days before the next billing period.

MICHELLE, THE FOUNDER AND OWNER OF SURFS UP, IS EXCITED TO BRING YOU HER NEWEST CREATION: A PERSONALLY CURATED SUBSCRIPTION BOX THAT CELEBRATES THE FOUR SEASONS IN A WAY ONLY SURFS UP CAN!
As a Surfs Up Candle Box Subscriber, youll receive a package filled with special surprises four times a year  Spring, Summer, Fall and Winter  that will feature items like mason jar candles, paint can candles, bath and body products, accessories and other fan-favorites!*
Your Spring box will include a mixture of soft, inviting scents and popular florals to help you make the much anticipated transition from winter into April Showers and May Flowers!
Get ready for the sun, beach and sand with some of our signature scents and vintage, ocean vibes with your Summer box.
Fall Scaries?! You wont have anything to fear when you receive your Fall box that taps into your love of sweater weather, hot apple cider and pumpkin patches.
Have you been naughty or nice? At Surfs Up, youre automatically on our nice list and your Winter box will be your favorite present! Snuggle up to the yulelog (real or fake!) with our best winter scents - think fresh pine needles, hot cocoa, mistletoe, holiday cookies and more!
*Box will not include every item listed or pictured and may include other items not listed or shown. The items listed and pictured are meant to provide an idea of what may be included season to season. Actual contents will vary, but we dont think youll be disappointed!
  By subscribing, you are agreeing to being a member and getting charged for at least three subscription boxes. See terms and conditions for more detailed information. 
The one-time purchase is valid for a single box. The box you receive will depend on the date of purchase. See below schedule for more details on which box to expect.
Automatic Payment and Shipping Schedule for Subscribers
You will be charged for your first box at time of checkout, and it will be shipped within 7-10 business days. Once you subscribe, you will be automatically placed on a standardized seasonal, 3-month payment and shipping schedule starting with your second box. See below for payment and shipping schedules based on the date you originally subscribed. 
If you subscribe between January 1st and April 1st, you will receive your first box (the Spring box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on June 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
If you subscribe between April 2nd and July 1st, you will receive your first box (the Summer box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on September 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
If you subscribe between July 2nd and October 1st, you will receive your first box (the Fall box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on December 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
If you subscribe between October 2nd and December 31st, you will receive your first box (the Winter box) in 7-10 business days. Your next box will be charged to your account on March 1st and shipped within 2-3 business days, and every 3 months thereafter on the first of the month.
Terms and Conditions
Due to COVID-19 safety guidelines, members may experience shipping delays. The Surfs Up Candle subscription box is a service that will be billed based on the option chosen. The two options we offer are 1) seasonally, four times a year with an automatic charge of $59.99 + $7 flat rate shipping using the payment method provided or 2) a one-time charge of $119.98 + free shipping for a single subscription box based on the season in which you purchase (see detailed calendar for exact dates). Foreign exchange or transaction fees may apply for non US customers. If youd like to cancel your subscription, you can do so after your third subscription box is fulfilled. After that, you can cancel no later than14 days prior to the next billing period. To cancel please contact Surfs Up Candle Subscription Box Customer Service at subscriptions@surfsupcandle.com.
  Please note: subscription box returns will not be accepted, and once the subscription is charged it cannot be refunded or cancelled. Cancellations must occur 14 days before the next billing period.
